Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再溫柔一點成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經夠溫柔了
